{"tid":1800942,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【聖誕豪客】大陸客逾4,000萬掃尚‧珒溋 交稅千萬","createTime":"2019-12-28T09:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T10:55:12.000Z","uid":267488,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ea5a21f8e72e64a67a3187583498b38f7c9e22ba","tid":1800942,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"本港政局不穩，內地客仍勇於大手掃貨。過去兩日聖誕假期，一手市場錄得十多宗成交，其中龍湖（960）及合景泰富（1813）合作發展的啟德尚．珒溋，昨連環沽出四伙，包括有內地客豪擲逾4,000萬元連購三伙。<br />\n<br />\n龍湖集團香港營銷總監黃少鴻稱，尚．珒溋昨獲大手客垂青，連環認購單位，成交金額達5,700萬元。消息指，其中2座21至23樓D室三伙，實用557方呎，全屬三房間隔，獲內地客大手買入，若以即供最大折扣計，成交價料約4,100萬元，平均呎價約2.4萬元。據知買家沒有香港身份證，須支付樓價30%印花稅，聖誕買樓豪交1,230萬元辣稅。尚．珒溋至今累售253伙，套現逾35億元。<br />\n<br />\n說好的攬炒呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553e32feb689e35c71ededd8af2e76ba0307fa8a","tid":1800942,"uid":68598,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:27:11.000Z","msg":"支那人走錢點阻<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd00eef78304d28a8d6e5bc8f45942a9f789469f","tid":1800942,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:27:23.000Z","msg":"投票： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhDfcr3wCsprrvnC37&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPBdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=caa2316c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37</a><br />\n<br />\n【最後4日】2020全民票選十八區區議會主席與發言人－民主統戰部<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800922</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phk5doO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fphk5doO.jpg&h=40b71bc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae3efe0f6a6e7ee2af1f930ecb386174b0f753c9","tid":1800942,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":